1. CompreFace — face recognition engine
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
LIWAN bundles and runs the CompreFace recognition engine as its recognition core
("Liwan Vision Engine" in product materials). The compose services
liwan-engine-api, liwan-engine-admin, liwan-engine-core, and liwan-engine-ui in
docker-compose.yml run the official, unmodified CompreFace images. LIWAN calls
CompreFace over its HTTP API and does not modify the CompreFace source.

